---
title: HelloHero: Seared Chicken Strips & Rainbow Couscous with Dill & Parsley Mayonnaise
description: This fresh and tasty meal features classic spices in an easy marinade for tender chicken breast, while carrot and greens bring colour and flavour to fluffy couscous. Sit back and enjoy this delicious meal that boasts every colour of the rainbow!

